All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
CompletionObserver
This is an implementation of the Observer patter which makes use of an interface to notify the Transporter to move the product to the list of completed products.
Configuration
The Configuration class is for the purpose of some common configurations required for the system to work.
Main
 
Oven
This is the main class in the system which represents a single oven worker.
Product
The Product class refers to the items that come into the system for the purpose of getting in the oven.
Scheduler
The scheduler is tasked with keeping track of all the ovens and assigning any new products that come into the system to the next best oven.
Transporter
To keep track of the completed products.
